data.description: 55+ COMMUNITY! NEWLY REMODELED! This is a lovely condominium home located in the Sunrise Village Community with plenty of shopping and restaurants within a short distance. This 2 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom home offer a well-designed floor plan.  Each bedroom feature recess lighting, along   with individual access to the private patio through a large glass sliding door.  This home has been newly upgraded - featuring vinyl plank flooring, a custom gas fireplace, with beautiful tile facing, upgraded and inviting kitchen featuring freshly painted cabinets, quartz counter tops and more.  Each bathroom has also been beautifully upgraded and remodeled. The interior laundry closet includes a stackable washer & dryer set, and offers plenty of storage closets.  Sunrise Village 55+ Community offers many added features for the community and residents. Enjoy the private community pool and spa, clubhouse and more.  Looking for a place to call home? This may be it.
